entries.femaleVariant: Nobody gets through this door, do you understand? Not a fuckin' soul.
You got it, boss. Nobody.
What the-- Who the fuck are you?! How'd you get in here?!
Simmer down – let's talk.
No. All you have to do is leave Night City. I'll tell 'em you took lead 'tween the eyes and none'll be the wiser. You can start over – a brand new life.
entries.maleVariant: No. All you have to do is leave Night City. I'll tell 'em you took lead between the eyes and none'll be the wiser. You can start over – a brand new life.

entries.femaleVariant: Leave Night City.
Yeah? Start with what? Everything I got's here – my club, staff, my girls...
Was that a yes or... a no?
entries.maleVariant: Was... that a yes or a no?

entries.femaleVariant: Just piss off and tell 'em the job's done.
Good idea. I'll save on bullets.
And everyone who wants you dead.
This isn't a multiple fuckin' choice. You're livin' on borrowed time.
entries.maleVariant: This isn't multiple fuckin' choice. You're livin' on borrowed time.

entries.femaleVariant: Shit! Motherfuckin' bleedin' cunt asshole!
Quiet down, or I'll have to cut our convo short.
Oh, I get it. Got a bounty on my head, have I? Who hired you? Militech? Asukaga? Or was it that wanker, Dino?
Eh, like it even matters. Find out myself when I yank that memory shard from your skull.
I'd like to see you try.
Go on. I'd like to see you try.
Siddown, Jack. I'm extending a fuckin' courtesy here. The fact that you're still alive means I'm open to parley.
Hah! Parley-vous go fuck yourself! Chit-chat's for assholes, so let's get it over and done with – you versus me, come on!
Say you win. Say you put me outta commission. You think your problems'll just vanish into thin air?
You crawled under a lotta people's skin. Said so yourself – Militech, Asukaga, Dino... They won't stop 'til your head falls at their feet.
So what? I'm s'posed to blow my fuckin' brains out?
Oh, good idea. You'd be savin' me lead.
entries.maleVariant: Good idea. You'd be savin' me lead.

entries.femaleVariant: Very fuckin' funny.
Good man. How's the missus? Recoverin' from those implants?
Doin' a lot better. Thanks for your help again, boss.
